room_title: Escape room "Arizona Shootout" by Escapology Lakeland in Lakeland
room_description: Travel back to Tombstone Arizona, 1881! You were just brainstorming with the group of local sheriffs to develop a new plan to round up the cowboy outlaws when you hear the screams. Quickly you pull out your gun and shoot one of the outlaws. The other two manage to vanish into thin air... Can you identify them in an hour, before they slip through your fingers?
